	<p>This edition and translation is based on <ref target="bibl:Chandra1919">Chandra 1919–1920</ref>. He writes: “This inscription is engraved in peculiar characters. The vertical lines of the n's is a little bent, and the lower part of m in mita is compressed.”</p>
